<div type="edition" xml:lang="ocm-Latn" rendition="class:83233 maturity:83213">            
            <ab xml:lang="san-Latn"><lb n="1"/><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <g ref="sym:floret" type="symbol">*</g> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Om̐ namaś śivāya <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <g ref="sym:floret" type="symbol">*</g> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></ab> 
<p><lb n="2"/><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakarāja <num value="977">977</num> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> kāla yām̃ po ku śrī parameśvaravarmmadeva punaḥ guhā niy·</p>
</div>
<div type="apparatus"/>
      <div type="translation" resp="part:argr">
         <p><foreign>Om</foreign> Homage to Śiva! <supplied reason="subaudible">Year of the</supplied> Śaka king:  977. <supplied reason="subaudible">This was</supplied> when his majesty Śrī Parameśvaravarmadeva repaired this cave.</p>
